eddos-desktop installs the requisite software to set up eddos as a desktop
operating system

WINDOW MANAGER
eddos currently supports the following window managers:
 * sway

User configuration is performed in the $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/sway directory, and
eddos utilities symlink to $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/eddos-sway

WEB BROWSER
firefox-wayland

PDF VIEWER
mupdf

MEDIA PLAYER
vlc

OFFICE SUITE
libreoffice


CUSTOMISATION
eddos removes plymouth, and rebuilds the kernel-core to update the initramfs
